'''''Second Sight''''' is a 1987 studio album by jazz [[double bass|bassist]] [[Marc Johnson (musician)|Marc Johnson]] released on the [[ECM Records|ECM]] label.<ref name="ECM discography">[http://www.ecmrecords.com/Catalogue/ECM/1300/1351.php ECM discography] accessed September 28, 2011</ref> 

==Reception==
The [[Allmusic]] review by [[Scott Yanow]] awarded the album 4 stars stating "This advanced unit performs eight group originals that cover a wide variety of moods, from introspective, spacy pieces to ones emphasizing fire and passion".<ref name="Allmusic">Yanow, S. [http://www.allmusic.com/album/second-sight-r141733 Allmusic Review] accessed September 28, 2011</ref>  
